Package gw.api.graph.traverse

Class GraphTraverserBase<T>

java.lang.Object
gw.api.graph.traverse.GraphTraverserBase<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
GraphTraverser<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
EntityGraphTraverser, GenericGraphTraverser, SubtypeGraphTraverser
public abstract class GraphTraverserBase<T> extends Object implements GraphTraverser<T>
Base implementation of GraphTraverser that handles visiting of nodes and graph cycles, but delegates the order of edge traversal to the subclass EdgeProvider implementation through the getEdgeProvider() template method.
Author:
bspies
